Shaping Chaos

Rank: 7
Uses: cantrip strand
      shape <object> <type> <detail>
Mana : varies (see "lore chaos2")

This is the ability of Bards to impose their will on raw chaos, temporarily
forcing it to match their view of reality.  It fell into disuse after
Saber's depature, and full understanding has not yet been reached.

See "lore chaos2" for what is known so far
